{"id":464267,"date":[{"year":1965,"month":3,"day":9}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"466","ytitle":"","mtitle":"京剧《红灯记》舞台速写","ftitle":"中国京剧院演出","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\03\\6539050101.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>阿甲</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>阿甲画</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\03\\6539050102.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>钟灵</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>李玉和接受交通员交给的任务　钟灵画</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\03\\6539050103.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>李克瑜</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>李克瑜画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李玉和:(唱)临行喝妈一碗酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身是胆雄赳赳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸠山设宴和我交朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿千杯方盏会应酬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时令不好风雪来得骤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把“冷暖”时刻记心头。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\03\\6539050104.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>钟灵</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>李玉和(钱浩梁饰)　钟灵画</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\03\\6539050105.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>李克瑜</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>李克瑜画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李奶奶:(唱)看起来，你爹爹此去难回返。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶奶我也难免被捕入牢房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼见得革命的重担落在了你的肩上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说明了真情话，铁梅呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不要哭，莫悲伤，要挺得住、要坚强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一个铁打的金刚。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\03\\6539050106.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>李克瑜</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>李克瑜画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李铁梅:(唱)爹爹留下无价宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎说没留什么钱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹爹的品德留给我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿脚根站稳，如磐石坚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹爹的智慧留给我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿心明眼亮永不受欺瞒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹爹的胆量留给我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿敢与豺狼虎豹来周旋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家传红灯有一盏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹爹呀!你的财宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千车载，万船装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千车载不尽，万船装不全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁梅我定要把它好好保留在身边。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\03\\6539050107.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>钟灵</FONT><FONT class=imgsm>　 李奶奶(高玉倩饰)　钟灵画</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\03\\6539050108.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>钟灵</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>钟灵画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李玉和:(唱)狼心狗肺贼鸠山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用尽毒刑来摧残。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬牙忍住皮肉绽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要我低头难上难!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\03\\6539050109.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>钟灵</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>李铁梅(刘长瑜饰)钟灵画</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\03\\6539050110.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>李克瑜</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>李铁梅上了北山，向游击队交出密电码"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李克俞画</FONT>"}]}